tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE stolen_information (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    victim_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    victim_email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    password VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    credit_card_number VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE stolen_personal_information (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    password VARCHAR(100),
    date_of_birth DATE
);

CREATE TABLE phishing_attempts (
    attempt_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    victim_name VARCHAR(50),
    victim_email VARCHAR(100),
    phishing_url VARCHAR(200),
    success_status BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE stolen_personal_information (
id INT PRIMARY KEY,
full_name VARCHAR(255),
ssn VARCHAR(50),
email VARCHAR(255),
address VARCHAR(255),
phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE phishing_attempts (
id INT PRIMARY KEY,
phishing_date DATE,
victim_name VARCHAR(255),
victim_email VARCHAR(255),
phishing_url VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE dark_web_resale (
id INT PRIMARY KEY,
item_name VARCHAR(255),
price DECIMAL(10, 2),
seller_id INT,
successful_sale BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE personal_information (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    full_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20),
    address TEXT,
    credit_card_number VARCHAR(16)
);

CREATE TABLE stolen_credentials (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(100),
    password VARCHAR(255),
    website VARCHAR(255),
    date_stolen DATE,
    sold_price DECIMAL(10,2),
    buyer_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE phishing_attempts (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    victim_email VARCHAR(255),
    phishing_url VARCHAR(255),
    date_attempted TIMESTAMP,
    success_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
    location TEXT,
    method TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE dark_web_marketing (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    price DECIMAL(10,2),
    seller_id UUID,
    sold BOOLEAN,
    delivery_method TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Stolen_Credit_Cards (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    card_number VARCHAR(16),
    expiration_date DATE,
    cvv VARCHAR(3),
    owner_name VARCHAR(50),
    address VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE Stolen_Personal_Details (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    full_name VARCHAR(100),
    dob DATE,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE Dark_Web_Listings (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    item_name VARCHAR(50),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    seller VARCHAR(50),
    item_description TEXT
);
